beer.beer_description: Made with big juicy Aussie and American hops, this luscious party pleaser is a cloudy fruit bomb full of delicious tropical juiciness. Before opening, roll the can to rouse the natural sediment, that may have settled over time. Unpasteurised for Natural Juicy Flavour. This beer is preservative free.
